title: Real Humans S1 Ep2
description:
Real Humans S1 Ep2

Trust No One - In a parallel present day, robots have become so human it is barely possible to distinguish them from real people. In this episode, a double murder is discovered in the old house where the rogue hubots charged their batteries and the police take up the hunt for the perpetrators. Inger has trouble accepting Anita, while at the same time money starts disappearing around the house. Roger's hatred of all hubots grows, especially the one his ex-wife lives with. Stars Andreas Wilson, Lisette Pagler and Pia Halvorsen. 

From Sweden, in Swedish 

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
